    <section id="shang">
      <h2>Shang Dynasty (<span class="chinese-char">商朝</span>, <em>Shāng Cháo</em>, c. 1600–1046 BCE)</h2>
      <p><span class="lang-en">The earliest dynasty confirmed by archaeological evidence, centred on the Yellow River in modern Henan. Its capital Yinxu (<span class="chinese-char">殷墟</span>, <em>Yīnxū</em>) yielded extraordinary finds.</span><span class="lang-tc">經考古證據確認的最早朝代，以今河南黃河流域為中心。其都城殷墟（<span class="chinese-char">殷墟</span>）出土了大量珍貴文物。</span><span class="lang-sc">经考古证据确认的最早朝代，以今河南黄河流域为中心。其都城殷墟（<span class="chinese-char">殷墟</span>）出土了大量珍贵文物。</span></p>
